{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After a few weeks, we have been transferred to Arlo, A-R-L-O, which is another close-lying country area, where we have been felling wood-- timber.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and we, we have been allocated a certain, certain [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] production minimum.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We have-- had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And others had to carry it down to the road from the hillside, where, where big, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] three-, four-ton trucks trucked it away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My duty there was there this, this, this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] carrying it down to the-- to the-- to the road.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember we came-- it was-- it was quite, quite, I mean, very, very hard work, but quite OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the morning, we came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, I remember, the guard would say, so you two, you four people here, well, you have to do that, that, and that-- these big hunks of things have been already there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we tried to get, get out of it by saying, oh, well, we can't do that over that, that, and that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we agreed that we do half of that and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's-- it was quite all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guards were Hungarian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were, were country teachers and of this background.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we have been directly responsible to, to Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-betweens, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember it was a fellow by the name of Fried Gezer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a-- I mean, we were 19 at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was 36 at the time, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- for days, they have been heartbroken and unapproachable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so we were responsible to him as such.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
